t excuse. The truth? You lack discipline.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "f3e7fd14-b8fe-af7f-a26e-afb35bcb7fee"], "hfbae2d0bg5d45g4282g8797g3be5319b70bc": ["Only my deity may guide me - not Vlaakith's spirit.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "45a12a3c-9f4c-7a87-cadc-eaa6efffd8ed"], "ha1412b51gcf4fg4f64gb44dgd5e92cac1c4c": ["I won't be participating.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "69fcdef1-5466-cfdc-6fab-bfc3ee626f8a"], "hde98bbc3gdfe9g482dg9020g83c371ec517d": ["<i>Mirror her ruthless stance.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "ae8a74fe-68e4-4558-36a0-aeb870ae0b54"], "hf3a3684fga731g4251gbd2cgd1a6b5cb9f5d": ["Yes. The Queen's spirit has entered you.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "67086001-b657-2a2a-7403-2b524919b56c"], "h8e79cccagaabag409ega2dcgfeff653acb41": ["<i>Tl'a'vlaakith, tavki.</i> Prove your tenacity.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "a164ad86-ae14-1337-e133-0b51136e05d8"], "h8b902fefg82c0g45a4gb000gccc516782a87": ["<i>Emulate Lae'zel's resolute stance.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "17e2fe6e-e6e6-2a1f-562d-96049b631975"], "h5f11446ag3ce3g4161g8fccg7730be7fec0e": ["Yes. Let the spirit guide your body.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "85302b33-ac8e-8c03-5804-4b4cd54d7219"], "he2e51f6fg8339g4a02gb3c5g5b75e3f074f6