on you.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "7ef9fad5-1a3a-e4ea-6ca6-91d75960498b"], "h9aea856dg6b0fg4ef5g91cagfc568b8eb157": ["Raphael will return. Temptation will whisper.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "b634ebeb-2954-21da-732a-78626e460ffd"], "h1f06d735gff38g45f1ga340g09a5232c78c8": ["And I fear you haven't the discipline to deny them.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "b3740b3d-40b3-bb6a-1d0e-90fe11d62287"], "h89235b0bg4a11g48efg99bfg6eed319e7e96": ["Mm - you have potential. In time you could master the <i>Tla'ket.</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "693e5695-a1da-dc24-85f5-c59e98a06b75"], "h20358fa9g7ecdg4bbcga966g98a8c1c2c385": ["*Your mind swims with worry. As long as this parasite infects you, you cannot be pure.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "34dea075-939c-0c09-0d36-293f22c08db6"], "h4bbd1b8cg892eg41e5gb944g79e8005b25c6": ["<i>Assume the third position</i>. Only in Vlaakith will I be cleansed.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "63723490-1e47-8257-a757-f16cfca23f17"], "ha687099bgdc8fg4876g8a48gf3723e03c8e3": ["<i>Still your mind and reflect on purity.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "97fa4dc7-d367-4438-7f93-6cead69a8f0d"], "h5ea8dda8g4d14g4616g9c20gfa95bcca66e3": ["<i>Back away.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "e3d2d8b2-c107-8d4c-20ca-00bd9b499aa4"], "h24e97aedge59dg4520gb92cgef6f803781bd": ["No. You have not heeded the spirit.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "8baceddd-1300-e882-c710-4e4d04af5654"], "h3a89c836g94d6g427fg9c1eg69656e86ed9b": ["<i>Take the second position. </i>No pain is so great as to defeat me.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "97871ee4-2455-c8ab-d1ef-fed7dc1a212d"], "h8b6d5d61gfae8g4bfcgababgfb95e752a058": ["*Vlaakith's spirit steels your bones. You will face all torment without fear.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "ee397c4a-a41d-4e34-2aa7-c5d3e9912cf4"], "h0929062eg15b6g4822gacb2g97d506fff12c": ["<i>Emulate Lae'zel's resolute stance.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "d5cee76a-43dc-8749-c4b8-7d913c6db5c6"], "h2c4c1b1ag6a2ag4af2g858ege2d4d7997cb1": ["<i>Back away.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "8aaa459b-b795-4edb-3a22-a0d1e40fa440"], "h45e0b12dgb156g4b09gbd67g4822340bc509": ["No. You have failed the Queen's spirit.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "4418d50c-1121-02b6-7272-024da5b0fd3d"], "h7b711b4bg7f11g4ba9gabe5g1468517119bc": ["<i>Take first position. </i>I will show my enemies no mercy.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "fb6512f2-ff2b-78c1-ded4-0ffc6d8e11b5"], "h356ed4c7g6338g434aga729gaa2be9d93cfe": ["*Vlaakith's spirit fills you. Your foes will know only the pain of death.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "97bb71db-3371-a111-8e4d-2a8bb40eb8b5"], "hd2e14a55g1e12g4bbdga8a7gdbd67f2a5e3b": ["<i>Mirror her ruthless stance.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "4b233f30-a571-2103-8c78-2a55c6742664"], "h4aa8a0e6g074bg4d61ga139gc88bc138420f": ["<i>Back away.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "39a2a31b-9524-07b2-cb71-0ad9d5a546c7"], "h6c4c734dgbe2cg422bgb3f8gc31627a6c062": ["As I suspected - you lack discipline.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "cf7b613f-9bc9-530b-fdba-6c1a879930bd"], "h147007acga31bg424dg97ccg5f7b1b22dece": ["Raphael will return. Temptation will whisper.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "a913822a-2db2-9fa4-f9f9-d226e59eb78f"], "hef56fbe2g5600g4371gbd4cg2d7b3ae5628c": ["And I fear you haven't the courage to deny either of them.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "7f9ccb9f-15b2-a56a-3c5d-47a73e0751e3"], "h2de4db05gfebbg4233g88aegb4e184295b87": ["May I join you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "2e5088ec-1402-3bba-10df-1ae87e329696"], "h211c482fgdaa3g4476gba4cg7a5ba157800f": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostHag_CRD_Laezel.html", "63b1ec5e-a65b-4db2-c09f-3d5d28e5ca03"]}